<br>
Our party of six squared off against the beast that gives a level 40 a hard time in solo, and soon 3 of our six were dead, and the other 3 (me, Kemi, and our healer) were soon to follow. I aggro'ed the beast onto me, and took off for a jog, to allow our cleric to have extra time to store up for some more heals. Kemi followed me (such a brave soul) which I was not expecting, and the beast jumped on her, and slayed her with some mighty smites.<br>
<br>
I got the beast on me again, and made my way back to our battered cleric. He had enough for two heals. This beast hit me for 96hp DMG in 1 second, and I came close to death again for a 3rd time. At the moment I feigned, the creature started to flee, just before I met my death deap in the South Karanas. With the help of the battered cleric we slayed him ... just in the nick of time.<br>
<br>
If it wasn't for the sacrifices of Kemi and Gumbrils chances are the battle would have been lost.<br>
<br>
It was a great and exciting battle, one that I will remember for some time!<br>
<br>
Raloth  <p><img src=http://www.canadiancommentary.com/yinyang.jpg></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/uraloth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raloth</A> at: 5/22/01 3:10:01 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/uaraegorne.showPublicProfile?language=EN>araegorne</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#8B4513>(5/22/01 11:24:15 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Massive Battle with an Aviak Avocet</span><hr size=1> I have fought these beasts Raloth and have seen many a warrior die at it's hands. They are fierce and not to be taken lightly. I have come close to meeting my end at the hands...feathers...whatever they use to hit! Hehe <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/uraloth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raloth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Administrator</span><br>  Posts: 471<br> <font color=#8B4513>(5/22/01 3:10:40 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.canadiancommentary.com/head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Massive Battle with an Aviak Avocet</span><hr size=1> Aye they can be a challenge for sure!<br>
